  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_2",
    "text": "1.位置优越",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10320781032078104,
      0.2536231884057971,
      0.2315202231520223,
      0.2740447957839262
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_3",
    "text": "(1)半球位置：东半球.北半球.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13296141329614133,
      0.2839262187088274,
      0.41841004184100417,
      0.30434782608695654
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_4",
    "text": "(2)海陆位置：亚洲东部.太平洋西岸 (3)纬度位置：大部分位于中纬度地区.属北温带.南部少数地区位于北回归线以南 的热带，没有寒带。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09298000929800093,
      0.2977602108036891,
      0.9381682938168294,
      0.4005270092226614
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_5",
    "text": "(4)位置优点",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1320316132031613,
      0.4090909090909091,
      0.26685262668526266,
      0.4281949934123847
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_6",
    "text": "我国地域广大.南北、东西气候差异大，为发展多种农业经 发展农业生产 济提供了有利条件. 对外交往与 东濒太平洋.多优良港湾，海上交通便利.有利于同海外各 国友好往来：西部深入亚欧大陆内部，与多国接壤，使我 合作 国陆上交通能与中亚.西亚、欧洲直接往来. 发展海洋事业 东临太平洋，沿海多优良港湾，便于开发各种海洋资源 其他 造就门我国丰富的旅游资源，如北国水雪.南国热带风光.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10227801022780102,
      0.4321475625823452,
      0.8526266852626685,
      0.647562582345191
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_7",
    "text": "2.国土订阔",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09112040911204092,
      0.6910408432147562,
      0.21385402138540213,
      0.7108036890645586
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_8",
    "text": "(1)陆地面积：约960万Km，差不多与整个欧的面积相等，仅次于俄罗斯.加拿大，在 世界各国中居第3位，是世界上面积较大的国家",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08554160855416086,
      0.7213438735177866,
      0.9214318921431892,
      0.7747035573122529
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_9",
    "text": "(2)领土四至",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12366341236634124,
      0.7852437417654808,
      0.2556950255695026,
      0.8036890645586298
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_55_10",
    "text": "最东：黑龙江与乌苏里江主航道中心线的相交处(135°E)； 最西：新疆的帕米尔高原(73°E)； 最南：南海的南沙群岛中的曾母暗沙(千°人)；",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
